Name: Junk Killer 110XFIRM Wheels
Short description: The Junk Killer wheel has a stiffer hub and a few top-secret “tweaks” under the hood, resulting in better roll, grip, and wear resistance.
Description:
Junk Killer 110XFIRM Wheels

We’ve got the new Junk Killer wheels!!

If you know JUNK, you know they're on a tireless pursuit of ultimate speed. 

This wheel has a stiffer hub and a few top-secret “tweaks” under the hood.

Killer Junk wheels have been extensively tested by top sprinters and endurance skaters. The result – they roll like a harder wheel while gripping like a softer one. Long-distance skaters have loved the extra roll for points and elimination races. And sprinters love it for that second half of the 1,000-meter races when they get the stanky leg.

What’s more, the natural hub, containing no pigments, has proven to outperform colored hubs. In tests, this resulted in better roll, grip, and wear resistance. As with all our other wheels, the urethane is also in its raw form – no additives or pigments added.

Powerslide 3X4 12.0/4x100 Black Gold 195 Frame

The Powerslide Triple X family just got a little bigger\, we are introducing the 3X4 100 - 12.0 Black Gold frame. 

For inline racers and intense athletes looking for control and stability\, the POWERSLIDE 3X4 100 - 12.0 Black Gold is the frame for you! 

It has a length of 12.0"/325mm\, and the frame is designed for young athletes in need of a high-performance inline racing frame. 

Made of the highest quality aircraft aluminum that’s CNC machined to perfection\, the frame is incredibly light while not compromising strength or style.

Complete with the trusty 195mm mount\, the frame can fit on a wide range of boots\, allowing you to easily find the perfect setup for your skating style.

On the track\, the POWERSLIDE 3X4 100 - 12.0 Black Gold frame will help you pass on the inside or outside like no other frame out there. Black Gold\, not your color? No worries! The frame is also available in a Titanium Blue colorway.

Name: Riedell Elara Ice Black Skate Boot
Short description: The NEW Riedell Elara boots have it all to help reach your highest goals.
Description:
Riedell Elara Ice Competitive Skate Boots
 
The NEW Riedell Elara Ice boots have it all to help reach your highest goals. 
 
It features:
  • Snug heel fit for better control
  • Lightweight uppers
  • The EVA cushion midsole provides great impact absorption.
  • Lightweight Hydro-Shield outsole
  • Abrasion-resistant and cut-resistant
  • Shortened outsole design allowing consistency for blade sizing
  • Allows for better fit and wrap around the ankle and top
  • Ergonomically shaped boot promotes a proper range of motion, support, and comfort.
  • Easier break-in
  • Contours to the shape of the foot. No heat molding required
  • Breathable polyurethane sock liner for improved moisture protection and durability
  • Abrasion- and wear-resistant top covering
  • Cork-leather heel, increasing height for a better forward position on the blade and impact absorption.
     
  • Size: 4–10 full and half sizes; EvoFit 2A/3A, EvoFit B/A, EvoFit D/C
 
Support Rating: 100
The hydroshield outsole as pictured on the Elara and Vega models is being discontinued. As stock is depleted, the Elara and Vega boots will undergo a running change to the outsole material. White boots will now receive a cinnamon midsole, a leather sole, and a cork/leather heel. Black boots will receive a black three-quarter midsole, a black leather sole, and a cork/leather heel.

Features
Riedell Elara Ice skate Boots:

The Riedell Elara offers top level figure skaters ultimate in support and lightweight performance. It was made with the newest materials and designs. A pre-formed fit gives a better wrap around the ankle, allowing for easier break-in and better fit right out of the box. 

With the shortened outsole design and increased heel height, this boot provides better maneuverability and position on blade. Moisture and abrasion resistant microfiber uppers and hydro-shield outsole give the boot longer performance. Elara uses the new Evofit last, which provides a broader toe shape for added fit and comfort. 

Impact absorbing EVA cushion midsole, cork heel and padded footbed make sure that skaters are training with the best possible ergonomics on landings. 

Elara is the culmination of ultimate performance, without compromising in skaters’ ergonomics and health.

PLEASE NOTE: Blade is not included.

Bont Semi Race III Inline Skate with Supercell Frame
Short description: The Bont Semi-Race III is made for skaters who want to skate fast and do it comfortably.
Description:
Bont Semi Race III Inline Skate
 

The Bont Semi Race III is the boot that defined the category. Bont designed this boot for skaters who wanted something in between a racing boot and a recreational skate. This skate is made for skaters who want to skate fast and do it comfortably. 

The new Bont Semi Race 3 has a rigid plastic cuff for the first time for added stability. The boot still retains a very soft rear cuff for forward flexion, and it has large V’s cut in the front lace area, which also aids forward flexion.

Start training with the Bont Semi-Race III inline racing skate!  

Regarding all Bont boots or skates, in many cases they will be in stock in the warehouse in Florida, but they could also be in Asia.

If in Asia, we could expect 2 to 4 weeks for delivery; we will only find out after the order is placed, and we will let you know by email.

  • Naturally bonds to the core during casting process

Attribute 3 value(s):
Piper VIE Outdoor Wheels

VIE\, where the momentum of inertia meets the road. Ultra-high-performance competition wheels. 

Piper has dominated the road over the years through unique formulas and core combinations. Vie left its traditional road technology behind\, and it's starting with Piper’s Disc technology. Moving most of the mass to the outer rim creates a momentum of inertia\, better known as rotational inertia. The disc has a unique spoke pattern and reinforced engineered thermoplastic content that provides responsive handling and steerability not available in their previous road wheels. Duo Technology is the central engine that separates Piper wheels from others.

VIE – M-Disc is made with reinforced engineered thermoplastic content that provides a firm-flex\, responsive handling and steerability not available in our previous road wheels. Duo Technology is the central engine that separates us from others. 

Features:

  • M-Disc: firm-flex & steerability
  • Duo-Tech: 2-n-1 (Two wheels in one)
  • More pop more roll
  • Insane-A-Thane: Magnifies energy & longevity.
  • Size: 110 M-Disc 74mm core/speed profile

From Hyper Octane to Atom IQ to our most current Duo-Tech\, Neal Piper has redesigned\, retooled\, and reinvigorated a new generation of racing wheels…again!

Neal is well known for his ability to provide the flat-track market with superior & consistent race formulas. 


Features:

  • DUO-TECH: 2-n-1 Two wheels in one\, click here to learn more about Duo-Tech
  •  Inside wheel: Super Charged formula\, maximizing energy

  • Voodoo Thane: Legendary flat-track indoor race formula “The original”

Name: Piper LEGEND PRO Roller Skate Wheels 63.5MM
Short description: Legend Pro is our ultra high-performance track wheel designed to re-define grip and dominate indoor flat track racing.
Description:
Piper LEGEND PRO Roller Skate Wheels 63.5MM
Neal Piper brings back his prolific Voo Doo Thane exclusively for Piper Wheels.  A lost art since Neal left the Hyper Cannibal program.  The return of Voo Doo Thane is one of the most exciting things to happen in the roller skate world - especially for those that speed skate. Crack the pack and take in that smell we are all so familiar with. Legend Pro is our ultra high-performance track wheel designed to re-define grip and dominate indoor flat track racing. 63.5 increases the amount of urethane on the core: more speed, more grip, smoother ride. Overall better performance!
  • Voo-doo thane: Legendary flat-track indoor race formula "The Original"
  • 7050 T-6 heat treated aluminum.
  • Galactic 44mm aluminum core.
  • Precision slip fit bearing seats (bearing press recommended)
  • Speed lip, maximum control and grip.
  • 63.5mm X 44 wide
  • Sold as 8 packs.
Note: Legend wheels must be broken in before coemption use, Piper suggests they are broken in organically for best results.
 
New and Ready to ship
 
Come in pack/8

Name: Bont Semi Race III Inline Skate with Supercell Frame X 4
Short description: The Bont Semi-Race III is made for skaters who want to skate fast and do it comfortably.
Description:
Bont Semi Race III Inline Skate
 

The Bont Semi Race is the boot that defined the category. Bont designed this boot for skaters who wanted something in between a racing boot and a recreational skate. This skate is made for skaters who want to skate fast and do it comfortably. 

The new Bont Semi Race 3 has a rigid plastic cuff for the first time for added stability. The boot still retains a very soft rear cuff for forward flexion, and it has large V’s cut in the front lace area, which also aids forward flexion.

Start training with the Bont Semi-Race III inline skate with the super light Supercell frame.

Regarding all Bont boots or skates, in many cases they will be in stock in the warehouse in Florida, but they could also be in Asia.

If Asia, we could expect 2 to 4 weeks for delivery; we will only find out after the order is placed, and we will let you know by email.

S1 Lifer Replacement Visor Iridium Gradient Mirror

Visor Specs:

• High Impact Polycarbonate to Prevent Shattering on Impact

• UV Protection

• Optically Correct Lens

• Anti-Fog Coating on the inside of the Visor to help prevent fogging

• Anti-Scratch Coating on the Outside of the Visor to help prevent minor scratches and nicks

• Patented "Cover Catcher" to allow for Multiple Helmet Covers to be worn with easy on off 


Visors can only be mounted to S1 Gen 2 Lifer Visor helmets. They cannot be mounted to standard Lifer helmets\, Retro Lifers\, Lifer Full Face\, Mini Lifers or Mega Lifers\, or any other brand of helmet.
